Post.title: About Me
Post._content:
Im an Hacker and an Builder.

I work on [Commutifi](http://www.commutifi.com/)

My last startup was [Broid](https://github.com/broidHQ/integrations) and was acquired.

I love helping people around the world with their companies, big or small. Solving issues!
My email is [b@iss.am](mailto:b@iss.am) or Twitter [@killix](https://twitter.com/killix). 

I also [write](/archives) sometimes, less than sometimes.

Post.title: Blog Changelog
Post._content:
# 2020-04-19

I thought it was time to change. Now the website is powered by [hexo] (https://hexo.io/).

Little reminder, before I used a mix of Ghost and [github.io] (killix.github.io).

In the operation, I did not take the time to migrate all (few) articles to this new version. I will do it quietly during the year.
